  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This update includes a few bug fixes\u00a0for the new features in 1.7.4</p><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.1-InventoryCountSheet\">Inventory Count Sheet</h3><ul><li><p>Save &amp; Submit is not submitting the last counted item - the counted item in the &quot;Current Item&quot; section would not always be submitted with the &quot;Save &amp; Submit&quot; action. This has been fixed.</p></li><li><p>UPC scan is pulling in deleted\u00a0catalog items - fixed.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.1-InventoryCountReconciliation\">Inventory Count Reconciliation</h3><ul><li><p>When all serials are valid, &quot;Save and Mark Reconciled&quot; button was not active. Fixed.</p></li><li><p>Improved the pop-over\u00a0window sizing</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.7.4.1-CustomFormSettings\">Custom Form Settings</h3><ul><li><p>Form preview -\u00a0you could select more than one radio button value. Fixed, now you can only select one value for each radio button in the preview window. <em>NOTE: this issue did not affect actual forms (i.e. forms you fill out and save on tickets)</em></p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
